title: Urbanization in Malaysia 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: In general Share of urban population in total population has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2010 to 2011.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2010 and 2011.
The highest Share of urban population in total population, of value 71.61 was reached at Year 2011
Minimum Share of urban population in total population about 70.91 was reached at Year 2010
